ygData.messageBody:
Ok here are a few things that may or may not
help~ I remeber tryimg to talk a freind through set up
not to long ago & he had this exact problem. After
going through everything step by step we found out that
he never checked a perferred method of payment.
Sounds funny but he said after downloading & doing his
account/logon info it shot him back to the start menu~ so he
kept hit play everquest & nothing. Wish I were in from
of my home pc to help but Im unfortunatly at work.
Email me if u like & I will try to further help u
out!<br>billy.scott@...
